# Logical Volume Manager
    - Logical Volume Manager

# Flexible Capacity
    - you can create file sys that extend across multiple devices.

    - multiple storage device into single Logical Volume

    - Exnted & shrink in Real Time.

# Data Mirror
    - increase fault tolerance & reliability
    - can create more than 1 copy of other device

    - replica

# Snapshot:
    - create point-in-time snapshot of your filesystems.

# LVM abstraction:
    - LVM add level of adstraction
    -   Logical Volume
        Volume Group
        Physical Volume
        Storage Devices